<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是讓人期待已久的萬聖節啦——！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<delay8 />來看看我到時候
能收集到多少糖果，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於到<delay8 />萬聖節這一天啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你準備好了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天島上的大家<delay8 />
都會為了糖果拿出真本事來！<delay40 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要做好覺悟迎接活動喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了能跑得更快，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近可是每天<delay8 />都在訓練下盤喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是萬聖節，我要展現出我的訓練成果。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你等著看吧——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">已經進入萬聖節活動前的<delay20 />
倒數計時階段了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的身心<delay8 />都準備好了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會<delay8 />全力以赴！<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可別嚇到<delay8 />腿軟啊——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">萬聖節終於要開始了！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糟了，<delay20 />我怎麼開始發抖了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這、<delay8 />這可不是因為害怕喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糖果好了，<delay20 />服裝好了！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好——！<delay8 />我準備好了！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬聖節，<delay8 />放馬過來吧！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說回來，<delay20 />我隨處可以看到
一些南瓜裝飾，<delay20 /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那難道是
萬聖節的東西嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />南瓜本身還挺重的，<delay8 />我還以為<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是有人用來代替槓鈴健身，<delay20 />
用完就丟在那裡喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得<delay8 />最近每當看到南瓜裝飾，<delay20 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就有種萬聖節逐漸逼近的感覺，<delay8 />
害我有點著急啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了能使出全力獲取糖果，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我得在萬聖節當天以前，<delay8 />
把我的步伐練得更加輕盈才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />島上的裝飾還真是增加了不少啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />照這樣下去，<delay20 />萬聖節當天，<delay8 />
島上應該會到處都是南瓜喔——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />南瓜裝飾<delay8 />增加超多的！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有種萬聖節即將到來的感覺，<delay20 />
我開始興奮起來啦——！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接著就只剩等到活動當天了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可要做好活動準備<delay20 />
跟心理準備喔？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>